{"tid":2036100,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港交所指暫有18間未錄盈利生物科技公司集資440億元","createTime":"2020-05-26T09:18:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T16:13:25.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4c836661f7c1e284da8d068013bc4e2290910578","tid":2036100,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:18:06.000Z","msg":"港交所指暫有18間未錄盈利生物科技公司集資440億元<br />\n26.05.2020 17:06<br />\n<br />\n港交所(<a href=\"http://00388.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00388.HK&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMAxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=76ce55cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00388.HK</a>)上市主管陳翊庭表示，自交易所2018年修改上市制度，容許未有盈利的生物科技公司上市後，目前共有18間生物科技公司循新制度上市，集資規模達440億元，當中有製藥、生物科技、醫療設備公司，部份更有加入研究及生產應對新型冠狀病毒疫情的藥物，她相信會有更多類型公司循新制度上市。<br />\n<br />\n陳翊庭在一個網上峰會上指，香港有更多投資銀行家、律師等專業人士參與生物科技公司上市，相信未來港交所將為生物科技營造一個新生態環境，而目前制度才剛起步發展，港交所會不斷審視並改進制度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1290706&amp;csid=261_368\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1290706%26csid%3D261_368&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMAxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=1ab41784\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1290706&amp;csid=261_368</a>"},{"pid":"acc177e43867417693e43ce8e0c49b2598966045","tid":2036100,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:19:43.000Z","msg":"港股又有新野玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa50601f33cbee2200a788b9721c1799a202de3b","tid":2036100,"uid":166462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:20:12.000Z","msg":"真香"},{"pid":"be51402e4d0f0a451122b3d17eb04923695b8f94","tid":2036100,"uid":1086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:23:09.0